                                    <div class="image-wrapper">
                                        <img 
                                            class="object-fit" 
                                            srcset="/img/chapter-lobby/modal-defined-zones/01_Arrival/05_Style@0,5x.jpg 338w,
                                                    /img/chapter-lobby/modal-defined-zones/01_Arrival/05_Style.jpg 675w" 
                                            src="/img/chapter-lobby/modal-defined-zones/01_Arrival/05_Style.jpg" alt="Style modal image">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="section__content">
                                        <h2 class="all-caps">Style</h2>
                                        <p>The perfect sense of arrival will tell the story of the hotel. We tell a conceptual story, one rooted in context and inspired by location. The Guest is welcomed into an intriguing and inviting space that feels like a home away from home. The outdoor areas reflect the hotel’s location; the entrance has a detailed front door; the entry vestibule should have a warm and comforting appearance.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </section>
